This can be rewritten as `(Xά╡λ έΙΗ Xέ▒╝) έΙσ Y`.

Since `IsNIPWith d έΗΣΏζΥΤ`, for the sequence `XέΓΒ, XέΓΓ, ...`, there exists `i < j` such that `Xά╡λ έΙΗ Xέ▒╝ έΛΗ Z` for some `Z` with `#Z έΚν d`.
